00:08:41.470 --> 00:08:43.071
but this really should be a line.

00:08:43.532 --> 00:08:46.862
This really should be a line.

00:08:47.601 --> 00:08:50.003
Maybe I'll ... Well, that's my best.

00:08:50.741 --> 00:08:52.876
I don't want to have to
re-plot all the points,

00:08:52.876 --> 00:08:54.602
but this should be a line like that.

00:08:54.602 --> 00:09:00.803
Every time we moved up 1, we went down 1.

00:09:00.803 --> 00:09:03.791
Every time we moved up 1, we moved down 1.

00:09:03.791 --> 00:09:04.806
We see that over here.

