00:10:32.066 --> 00:10:32.875
So let me plot that

00:10:32.875 --> 00:10:34.202
and I'll try to plot
that a little bit neater

00:10:34.202 --> 00:10:36.027
so it's clear that this is a line.

00:10:37.611 --> 00:10:41.702
That's my marginal product revenue.

00:10:41.702 --> 00:10:42.802
You could also view that

00:10:42.802 --> 00:10:46.076
as the marginal benefit
calculated in terms of dollars.

00:10:46.076 --> 00:10:47.334
You could view this as a marginal benefit

00:10:47.334 --> 00:10:48.469
in terms of cars washed.

00:10:48.469 --> 00:10:51.334
This is the marginal
benefit in terms of dollars.

