This is my quantity of labor

00:11:15.282 --> 00:11:17.386
and the marginal product
revenue goes up to 25.

00:11:17.386 --> 00:11:22.925
Let's say this is 5, 10, 15, 20 and 25.

00:11:24.539 --> 00:11:26.471
Halfway between zero and 1 person,

00:11:26.471 --> 00:11:28.341
so this is 25 right over here.

00:11:28.341 --> 00:11:32.202
I am producing $25, or
I get an incremental

00:11:32.202 --> 00:11:35.074
